# Vibe-Code-Adaptive-Game-AI Project Structure

This project is an advanced AI fighting game built with Phaser 3 featuring two Q-learning AI agents.

## Core Files

- **Main Game Logic**: [src/main.js](mdc:src/main.js) - Contains the PlayScene class with all game mechanics
- **AI Implementation**: [src/RL.js](mdc:src/RL.js) - Q-learning agent implementation for both characters
- **Game Entry Point**: [index.html](mdc:index.html) - Main HTML file that loads the game
- **Dependencies**: [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Node.js dependencies and scripts

## Configuration Files

- **Hero AI Config**: [heroknight.json](mdc:heroknight.json) - Learning parameters for hero knight AI
- **Purple Knight Config**: [pknight.json](mdc:pknight.json) - Learning parameters for purple knight AI
- **Python Backend**: [game_event_microservice/ai_bridge_fastapi.py](mdc:game_event_microservice/ai_bridge_fastapi.py) - FastAPI backend for data collection

## Asset Organization

- **Character Sprites**: [assets/character/](mdc:assets/character/) - All character animations and sprites
- **Map Assets**: [assets/map/](mdc:assets/map/) - Environment textures and backgrounds

## Key Technologies

- **Game Engine**: Phaser 3 framework
- **Physics**: Matter.js integrated with Phaser
- **AI**: Q-learning reinforcement learning
- **Backend**: FastAPI with ChromaDB for data collection